| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-2578 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomhub)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 27949ced-25a9-5d7c-8986-3e7a2fb0fef5"
